summary: This is the header file for the TCFeedback class in the SMG_NothingIsAll project, which contains four feedback methods: feedbackTIR, feedbackTIP, feedbackTOR, and feedbackTOP. These methods are used to handle different types of feedback related to short-match models, fo nodes, and cmv nodes. The author notes that these methods have been updated on specific dates in the past.
